==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sporophyte
<hw>Spo"ro*phyte</hw> <pr>(sp⟦omac⟧"r⟦osl⟧*f⟦imac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Spore</ets> + Gr. <grk>fyto`n</grk> plant.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>In plants exhibiting alternation of generations,
the generation which bears asexual spores; -- opposed to
<contr>gametophyte</contr>. It is not clearly differentiated in the life
cycle of the lower plants.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Spo`ro*phyt"ic</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

